00:27:04,000 --> 00:27:05,590
Here you are, hold it carefully.

574
00:27:06,070 --> 00:27:06,710
Yes...

575
00:27:06,740 --> 00:27:07,310
Be careful.

576
00:27:07,350 --> 00:27:07,830
I will...

577
00:27:07,870 --> 00:27:08,850
Alright...

578
00:27:08,950 --> 00:27:09,620
Take it slow on the road.

579
00:27:09,660 --> 00:27:10,370
Okay!

580
00:27:19,280 --> 00:27:21,340
Rice wine! Who wants some rice wine?

581
00:27:38,200 --> 00:27:39,350
Studying?

582
00:27:51,610 --> 00:27:52,550
If you have this much spare time,

583
00:27:52,550 --> 00:27:54,840
you might as well memorize a few more English words.

584
00:27:54,860 --> 00:27:55,670
I've finished that.

585
00:27:56,250 --> 00:27:57,700
Have you done your math homework?

586
00:27:57,720 --> 00:27:59,040
I finished it yesterday.

587
00:28:09,640 --> 00:28:11,080
Siyi hasn't come lately, has she?

588
00:28:11,110 --> 00:28:12,040
No,

589
00:28:12,480 --> 00:28:14,160
she hasn't shown up since that day.

590
00:28:18,610 --> 00:28:19,370
What's wrong?

591
00:28:20,130 --> 00:28:21,740
You should spend less time with her from now on.

592
00:28:22,360 --> 00:28:23,120
Why?

593
00:28:23,540 --> 00:28:24,890
Why so many questions?

594
00:28:25,590 --> 00:28:26,300
But...

595
00:28:26,600 --> 00:28:28,400
I just suggested

596
00:28:28,410 --> 00:28:30,270
she move in with us.

597
00:28:31,820 --> 00:28:33,130
It's for her own good.

598
00:28:33,180 --> 00:28:34,470
Don't you understand that?

599
00:28:34,510 --> 00:28:36,070
Those kids around her

600
00:28:36,070 --> 00:28:37,300
don't care about studying.

601
00:28:37,410 --> 00:28:39,830
I'm creating an opportunity for her

602
00:28:39,830 --> 00:28:41,230
to keep her distance from them.

603
00:28:41,940 --> 00:28:43,010
Mom,

604
00:28:43,180 --> 00:28:45,450
-are you crazy?
-Calm down.

605
00:28:58,160 --> 00:28:59,350
I'm doing this for your own good.

606
00:28:59,350 --> 00:29:00,750
I don't need it.

607
00:29:00,790 --> 00:29:02,990
Mom, I don't need it!

608
00:29:03,100 --> 00:29:05,240
Watch your mouth.

609
00:29:05,750 --> 00:29:08,480
Chen Rui, I know you're rebellious in puberty.

610
00:29:08,550 --> 00:29:09,800
You won't listen to your parents.

611
00:29:09,960 --> 00:29:11,680
But let me emphasize this again.

612
00:29:13,630 --> 00:29:16,260
From a farm girl with no background,

613
00:29:16,350 --> 00:29:17,510
I've fought my way to where I am today.

614
00:29:17,550 --> 00:29:18,950
What got me here?

615
00:29:19,110 --> 00:29:21,980
It was my incredible perseverance and self-discipline.

616
00:29:23,320 --> 00:29:24,570
You've gone too far!

617
00:29:34,740 --> 00:29:35,970
She's coming...

618
00:29:36,010 --> 00:29:36,960
There she comes...

619
00:30:17,140 --> 00:30:17,990
Chris,

620
00:30:18,240 --> 00:30:19,210
are you busy right now?

621
00:30:24,990 --> 00:30:25,870
It's okay.

622
00:30:26,220 --> 00:30:27,370
I'm recording songs

623
00:30:28,100 --> 00:30:29,880
for a new album.

624
00:30:43,340 --> 00:30:44,480
I'm looking forward to it.

625
00:30:47,920 --> 00:30:49,780
She's even acting cute.

626
00:30:57,460 --> 00:31:00,780
I'll be holding a concert in Chengdu next month.

627
00:31:00,820 --> 00:31:02,740
Can you come?

628
00:31:22,600 --> 00:31:23,320
Yes.

629
00:31:24,940 --> 00:31:26,300
Seriously?

630
00:31:33,270 --> 00:31:34,780
That's great.

631
00:31:34,970 --> 00:31:36,800
See you in Chengdu then.

632
00:31:36,980 --> 00:31:38,470
I'll be waiting for you.

633
00:31:41,460 --> 00:31:43,080
That scared me.

634
00:31:48,310 --> 00:31:49,490
It's a date.

635
00:32:00,140 --> 00:32:02,440
This girl will definitely come to borrow money from us soon.

636
00:32:02,460 --> 00:32:03,220
Do you believe it?

637
00:32:03,150 --> 00:32:06,790
[Cyber Surfing Café]

638
00:32:07,790 --> 00:32:09,150
You're laughing too loud!

639
00:32:10,750 --> 00:32:12,090
I don't have any money anyway.

640
00:32:12,120 --> 00:32:13,000
He has money!

641
00:32:13,030 --> 00:32:13,880
I don't.

642
00:32:13,920 --> 00:32:14,310
You don't?

643
00:32:14,310 --> 00:32:15,350
Look at your Max sneakers.

644
00:32:15,390 --> 00:32:16,310
Don't wear them anymore, okay?

645
00:32:16,310 --> 00:32:16,840
The heels are high.

646
00:32:16,870 --> 00:32:17,750
What are you doing?

647
00:32:19,080 --> 00:32:20,530
What's the matter?

648
00:32:20,560 --> 00:32:22,650
I've been curious about something.

649
00:32:23,670 --> 00:32:24,680
Go ahead.

650
00:32:24,790 --> 00:32:27,850
How many bones do you think a person has?

651
00:32:27,980 --> 00:32:29,100
If they're broken,

652
00:32:29,120 --> 00:32:30,890
how long would it take to heal?

653
00:32:33,790 --> 00:32:35,010
You...

654
00:32:35,680 --> 00:32:37,330
What do you mean?

655
00:32:40,110 --> 00:32:40,590
Stop...

656
00:32:40,630 --> 00:32:41,030
Fenghua...

657
00:32:41,030 --> 00:32:41,830
Let go!

658
00:32:41,890 --> 00:32:45,900
[Chatting with Fenghua]

659
00:32:48,390 --> 00:32:49,850
Do you think I'm a fool?

660
00:32:50,120 --> 00:32:50,710
Fenghua.

661
00:32:50,790 --> 00:32:51,590
He was just joking with you.

662
00:32:51,590 --> 00:32:52,300
How did you find out?

663
00:32:52,300 --> 00:32:53,850
Are you making a fool of me?

664
00:33:01,790 --> 00:33:02,670
I know.

665
00:33:04,640 --> 00:33:06,350
None of you like Chris.

666
00:33:07,830 --> 00:33:09,060
It's okay.

667
00:33:09,170 --> 00:33:11,340
No one is forcing you to like her.

668
00:33:11,980 --> 00:33:14,150
But you have no right

669
00:33:15,430 --> 00:33:17,280
to mock someone else's choices.

670
00:33:19,050 --> 00:33:20,290
Yes,

671
00:33:20,690 --> 00:33:22,680
I may not have the money

672
00:33:22,870 --> 00:33:25,010
to afford a concert ticket today.

673
00:33:25,060 --> 00:33:26,790
But one day,

674
00:33:26,860 --> 00:33:28,030
Chris will

675
00:33:28,070 --> 00:33:29,870
hold a concert in the world's

676
00:33:29,910 --> 00:33:31,070
largest stadium!

677
00:33:31,490 --> 00:33:32,740
And I,

678
00:33:33,380 --> 00:33:35,660
I will be able to afford

679
00:33:35,690 --> 00:33:37,450
a front-row seat by myself.

680
00:33:38,190 --> 00:33:40,350
I'll sit in the closest position to her,

681
00:33:40,380 --> 00:33:41,950
listening to her sing.

682
00:33:42,450 --> 00:33:44,810
This is the most serious promise

683
00:33:45,090 --> 00:33:46,900
I make to my future self!

684
00:33:48,450 --> 00:33:49,180
Fenghua.

685
00:33:49,210 --> 00:33:49,770
Fenghua.

686
00:33:49,790 --> 00:33:50,230
Fenghua!

687
00:33:50,260 --> 00:33:50,700
Fenghua!

688
00:33:50,730 --> 00:33:51,970
-Fenghua!
-Fenghua!

689
00:35:02,930 --> 00:35:04,600
Stinky tofu.

690
00:35:14,460 --> 00:35:15,330
What's wrong?

691
00:35:16,600 --> 00:35:17,730
Did you cry?

692
00:35:18,140 --> 00:35:18,980
No.

693
00:35:19,550 --> 00:35:21,150
Then why do you look so dejected?

694
00:35:22,760 --> 00:35:24,010
What happened?

695
00:35:24,030 --> 00:35:25,150
Really, it's nothing.

696
00:35:25,470 --> 00:35:26,110
Tell me.

697
00:35:29,760 --> 00:35:30,400
Mom,

698
00:35:31,630 --> 00:35:33,860
I just saw Siyi.

699
00:35:34,270 --> 00:35:36,520
I think she's working at Uncle Zhou's shop.

700
00:35:36,690 --> 00:35:37,750
What kind of work?

701
00:35:39,480 --> 00:35:41,170
It seemed to be food delivery.

702
00:35:41,190 --> 00:35:43,100
I hid and didn't dare to ask her.

703
00:35:43,140 --> 00:35:44,460
What's wrong with delivering food?

704
00:35:44,480 --> 00:35:45,870
Do you think it's a shame?

705
00:35:46,130 --> 00:35:47,080
Not at all.

706
00:35:47,150 --> 00:35:48,470
That's it!

707
00:35:48,750 --> 00:35:50,660
If she's not troubled,

708
00:35:50,680 --> 00:35:52,230
why didn't she tell me?

709
00:35:53,200 --> 00:35:54,740
You're so young,

710
00:35:54,780 --> 00:35:56,900
yet your mind is full of twists and turns.

711
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:58,340
You've watched too many TV dramas.

712
00:36:00,590 --> 00:36:02,200
Siyi always thinks too much

713
00:36:02,550 --> 00:36:05,030
and keeps everything to herself when she encounters difficulties.

714
00:36:05,800 --> 00:36:07,450
I really don't want to add to her stress.

715
00:36:07,470 --> 00:36:09,540
Madam, I want some mung bean cakes, please.

716
00:36:09,840 --> 00:36:10,710
Coming right up!

717
00:36:11,780 --> 00:36:13,460
If you're real besties,

718
00:36:13,480 --> 00:36:15,290
you'd better show some sincerity.

719
00:36:15,990 --> 00:36:17,070
Avoiding it

720
00:36:17,190 --> 00:36:18,590
won't fix anything.

721
00:36:19,330 --> 00:36:20,370
How old are you?

722
00:36:22,810 --> 00:36:23,690
None of your business.

723
00:36:27,710 --> 00:36:28,760
What are you doing?

724
00:36:29,510 --> 00:36:31,400
You really are photogenic.

725
00:36:42,910 --> 00:36:43,650
Siyi.

726
00:36:45,670 --> 00:36:47,590
This is our homemade salted pork.

727
00:36:47,590 --> 00:36:49,630
Use it to make a dish for your grandma tomorrow.

728
00:36:49,660 --> 00:36:50,630
No, thanks.

729
00:36:51,470 --> 00:36:52,910
It's for your grandma,

730
00:36:52,940 --> 00:36:54,180
not for you.

731
00:36:54,210 --> 00:36:55,010
Just take it.

732
00:36:55,910 --> 00:36:57,150
Thank you, Uncle Zhou.

733
00:36:57,180 --> 00:36:58,060
I'll head back now.

734
00:36:58,080 --> 00:36:58,610
OK.

735
00:36:58,990 --> 00:36:59,750
Be careful on your way.

736
00:36:59,780 --> 00:37:00,510
OK.

737
00:37:28,740 --> 00:37:29,710
Fenghua,

738
00:37:29,710 --> 00:37:31,780
you really scared me!

739
00:37:34,010 --> 00:37:35,070
Where have you been?

740
00:37:36,590 --> 00:37:37,310
The library.

741
00:37:38,880 --> 00:37:39,700
Nah,

742
00:37:39,720 --> 00:37:41,040
it doesn't smell like the library.

743
00:37:41,080 --> 00:37:43,310
It smells more like kitchen grease from a restaurant.

744
00:37:43,330 --> 00:37:44,250
Huaiyang cuisine.

745
00:37:44,770 --> 00:37:46,050
Go away.

746
00:37:46,850 --> 00:37:49,450
Is it worth working part-time at the cost of your studies?

747
00:37:53,250 --> 00:37:54,530
Don't worry,

748
00:37:55,050 --> 00:37:56,180
I won't tell your grandma.

749
00:37:58,630 --> 00:38:00,270
How did you know that?

750
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:04,760
Your hair smells like kitchen grease,

751
00:38:08,620 --> 00:38:10,640
and your hands smell like dish soap.

752
00:38:13,700 --> 00:38:14,620
And this.

753
00:38:15,470 --> 00:38:16,400
Did you buy it at the library?

754
00:38:18,740 --> 00:38:21,000
Don't tell anyone else, anyway.

755
00:38:21,030 --> 00:38:21,910
I won't say anything.

756
00:38:21,940 --> 00:38:23,700
Aren't you afraid Uncle Zhou will tell your grandma?

757
00:38:23,720 --> 00:38:24,470
He won't.

758
00:38:24,510 --> 00:38:26,210
I made him promise to keep it a secret.

759
00:38:29,350 --> 00:38:30,190
I have a better idea

760
00:38:30,190 --> 00:38:31,470
to make money.

761
00:38:31,490 --> 00:38:32,320
Want to give it a try?

762
00:38:32,950 --> 00:38:33,870
Not interested.

763
00:38:34,150 --> 00:38:34,910
Really?

764
00:38:34,930 --> 00:38:36,690
We received a photographer at my mother's stall.

765
00:38:36,720 --> 00:38:38,600
He said being a model makes money really fast.

766
00:38:38,950 --> 00:38:39,750
Model?

767
00:38:41,100 --> 00:38:41,980
Come on, let's go to my place.

768
00:38:42,000 --> 00:38:43,130
I'll show you.

769
00:38:46,880 --> 00:38:49,880
This guy takes photos for ads.

770
00:38:49,970 --> 00:38:51,730
He saw me and said I was photogenic enough

771
00:38:51,750 --> 00:38:53,300
to be a print model.

772
00:38:53,490 --> 00:38:56,410
A set of photos can be done in just a few hours.

773
00:38:56,450 --> 00:38:58,330
Eight hundred yuan, paid in cash.

774
00:39:01,490 --> 00:39:03,130
Sounds fishy.

775
00:39:05,610 --> 00:39:07,250
Fine, you'll see.

776
00:39:11,890 --> 00:39:13,900
Look, he took these random photos of me.

777
00:39:16,430 --> 00:39:17,440
What do you think?

778
00:39:18,270 --> 00:39:20,410
His skills are pretty good.

779
00:39:21,050 --> 00:39:23,310
The skills are not the key.

780
00:39:23,430 --> 00:39:24,700
It's all thanks to my good looks.

781
00:39:24,730 --> 00:39:25,740
I look great in anyone's camera.

782
00:39:30,740 --> 00:39:32,030
Are you really planning to try?

783
00:39:33,130 --> 00:39:34,440
It doesn't hurt to try.

784
00:39:34,660 --> 00:39:36,200
He has a studio in the city.

785
00:39:36,670 --> 00:39:38,230
I'll find time to check it out later.

786
00:39:40,190 --> 00:39:41,150
Would you go with me?

787
00:39:42,310 --> 00:39:43,710
He invited you.

788
00:39:43,730 --> 00:39:44,980
Why should I go?

789
00:39:46,470 --> 00:39:48,360
I'm a bit scared to go alone.

790
00:39:48,450 --> 00:39:49,810
What if it's a scam?

791
00:39:50,440 --> 00:39:52,160
Then ask Wanghe and the others to go with you.

792
00:39:53,490 --> 00:39:54,370
No.

793
00:39:55,030 --> 00:39:56,560
I'll have to pose for the photos.

794
00:39:56,590 --> 00:39:57,630
If those three see me like that,

795
00:39:57,650 --> 00:39:58,800
I'd die of embarrassment.

796
00:40:03,470 --> 00:40:05,190
Go with me, please.

797
00:40:05,390 --> 00:40:06,270
Let's go together

798
00:40:06,290 --> 00:40:07,240
and earn 800 per week.

799
00:40:07,270 --> 00:40:08,920
That's over 3,000 a month!

800
00:40:08,960 --> 00:40:10,730
Isn't that better than working at the restaurant?

801
00:40:14,420 --> 00:40:15,600
Don't worry.

802
00:40:15,670 --> 00:40:17,940
He even thinks I'm pretty.

803
00:40:18,080 --> 00:40:18,990
So imagine how he'll see you.

804
00:40:19,960 --> 00:40:20,990
You can take

805
00:40:21,020 --> 00:40:23,680
a few more sets and post them online later.

806
00:40:23,940 --> 00:40:26,090
You might become a famous model!

807
00:40:26,120 --> 00:40:28,280
Then you could charge several thousand for a set

808
00:40:28,440 --> 00:40:30,920
with your photos all over those websites.

809
00:40:30,960 --> 00:40:33,230
People might ask for your autograph on the street.

810
00:40:33,660 --> 00:40:36,290
Even Jay Chou might want you to star in his music videos.

811
00:40:40,160 --> 00:40:41,370
I'll think about it.

812
00:40:53,030 --> 00:40:53,840
Ms. Liang.

813
00:40:54,840 --> 00:40:55,630
Siyi.

814
00:40:56,830 --> 00:40:57,750
Let me help you.

815
00:40:57,770 --> 00:40:59,020
No, thanks. It's too heavy.

816
00:40:59,050 --> 00:41:00,420
So don't bother. I'll handle it.

817
00:41:00,750 --> 00:41:01,390
It's okay.

818
00:41:02,750 --> 00:41:03,370
You...

819
00:41:08,750 --> 00:41:09,760
Let me take it.

820
00:41:13,270 --> 00:41:13,870
Goodbye, then.

821
00:41:13,890 --> 00:41:14,660
Wait...

822
00:41:14,690 --> 00:41:16,770
Come in and have some water. C'mon.

823
00:41:21,820 --> 00:41:22,580
Take a seat.

824
00:41:23,800 --> 00:41:24,760
Where's Wanghe?

825
00:41:26,360 --> 00:41:27,730
Who knows?

826
00:41:27,760 --> 00:41:29,620
He's hanging out all the time, never at home.

827
00:41:30,450 --> 00:41:31,140
Here.

828
00:41:31,470 --> 00:41:32,480
Thank you.

829
00:41:32,810 --> 00:41:34,590
If he were as sensible as you,

830
00:41:34,670 --> 00:41:36,650
I would wake up laughing from my dreams.

831
00:41:37,050 --> 00:41:38,630
He just doesn't like studying.

832
00:41:38,660 --> 00:41:39,890
He'd surely score high if he were into it.

833
00:41:40,140 --> 00:41:41,400
Let him be.

834
00:41:41,650 --> 00:41:43,500
As long as he can graduate from high school.

835
00:41:45,520 --> 00:41:46,250
What about you?

836
00:41:46,670 --> 00:41:48,310
Have you decided which university to apply for?

837
00:41:48,630 --> 00:41:49,890
Honghuai Normal University.

838
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:52,810
Is it a key university?

839
00:41:54,060 --> 00:41:56,380
It's second-tier, but close to home.

840
00:41:56,410 --> 00:41:58,050
I can come home every week to be with my grandma.

841
00:42:12,400 --> 00:42:13,280
Good girl.

842
00:42:16,510 --> 00:42:17,270
But...

843
00:42:18,560 --> 00:42:19,950
Being too sensible isn't always good.

844
00:42:20,440 --> 00:42:23,400
You might suffer a lot in your life.

845
00:42:31,230 --> 00:42:32,030
Just drink it.

846
00:42:32,700 --> 00:42:33,830
Thank you, Ms. Liang.

847
00:42:33,870 --> 00:42:34,750
I'll take my leave.

848
00:42:35,980 --> 00:42:36,740
Bye-bye.

849
00:42:37,370 --> 00:42:38,480
Have a good rest!
